113683959e1fa5ea07c39","tid":1190444,"uid":19068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_sG6zbkyDUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_sG6zbkyDUU&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ugfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=52deb6e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_sG6zbkyDUU</a>"},{"pid":"beaee4d97e81135d7ae9bab543bfbedca49f867e","tid":1190444,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"823fe8ab29219197c6ffbeb2adcee60ecf77d13a","tid":1190444,"uid":5523,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"33c83e86c3822c5a9da5374785320e8832bcd7fe","tid":1190444,"uid":85456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413947648b541757d38f692d3e54c8c1676f3394","tid":1190444,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76986c2fc6305e67afd8304366d864b23aa489a0","tid":1190444,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"打到仆街同軍紀冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多惡人都好打得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"只係唔明點解屈原值得有端午節但岳飛無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"因為金人係共狗眼中都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"上面個咩skr我block左的<br />\n<br />\n《宋史&middot;岳飛傳》：<br />\n<br />\n飛至孝，母留河北，遣人求訪，迎歸。母有痼疾，藥餌必親。母卒，水漿不入口者三日。家無姬侍。吳玠素服飛，願與交驩，飾名姝遺之。飛曰：「主上宵旰，豈大將安樂時？」卻不受，玠益敬服。少豪飲，帝戒之曰：「卿異時到河朔，乃可飲。」遂絕不飲。帝初為飛營第，飛辭曰：「敵未滅，何以家為？」或問天下何時太平，飛曰：「文臣不愛錢，武臣不惜死，天下太平矣。」<br />\n<br />\n師每休捨，課將士注坡跳壕，皆重鎧習之。子雲嘗習注坡，馬躓，怒而鞭之。卒有取民麻一縷以束芻者，立斬以徇。卒夜宿，民開門願納，無敢入者。軍號「凍死不拆屋，餓死不鹵掠。」卒有疾，躬為調藥；諸將遠戍，遣妻問勞其家；死事者哭之而育其孤，或以子婚其女。凡有頒犒，均給軍吏，秋毫不私。<br />\n<br />\n善以少擊衆。欲有所舉，盡召諸統制與謀，謀定而後戰，故有勝無敗。猝遇敵不動，故敵為之語曰：「撼山易，撼岳家軍難。」張俊嘗問用兵之術，曰：「仁、智、信、勇、嚴，闕一不可。」調軍食，必蹙額曰：「東南民力，耗敝極矣。」荊湖平，募民營田，又為屯田，歲省漕運之半。帝手書曹操、諸葛亮、羊祜三事賜之。飛跋其後，獨指操為姦賊而鄙之，尤檜所惡也<br />\n<br />\n呢本就係正式史書<br />\n岳飛傳第一句就係人人都識既「岳飛字鵬舉」<br />\n<br />\n岳飛為國為民軍紀嚴明<br />\n無恥鼠輩唔好誣蔑岳飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48785797936a8437955df1322036e8fbfa2c8b6","tid":1190444,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf6bd79f2957e57385b4c323fc8c6bc4d27e2a91","tid":1190444,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a209be1441f777fa871a93d70436189c8fa935","tid":1190444,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"正史岳家軍唔係小說中咁守軍紀嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"但最後被泛民篤灰"},{"pid":"7d2703545c2ea72f501a1ff56c6967358e2a25e0","tid":1190444,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba28b05aedd1df203b391b3599d57b5fafec5d81","tid":1190444,"uid":7840,"like":11,"dislike":13,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dfe341cae788cf0bdbef63838aef8187b4d4fca2","tid":1190444,"uid":24457,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"1日12塊金牌 仲勁過巴菲特"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔係菲利咩"},{"pid":"5e8baa5df78ebe9dad1677cd9b8f82a1f48500ee","tid":1190444,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823fe8ab29219197c6ffbeb2adcee60ecf77d13a","tid":1190444,"uid":5523,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"33c83e86c3822c5a9da5374785320e8832bcd7fe","tid":1190